gobblin.runtime.instance

Class StandardGobblinInstanceDriver.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.instance.StandardGobblinInstanceDriver.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    StandardGobblinInstanceDriver

    public static class StandardGobblinInstanceDriver.Builder
extends Object
    A builder for StandardGobblinInstanceDriver instances. The goal is to be convention driven rather than configuration.

    Conventions:

    • Logger uses the instance name as a category
    • Default implementations of JobCatalog, JobSpecScheduler, JobExecutionLauncher use the logger as their logger.
